INSERT INTO system_index
            (
                system_id,
                manufacturing,
                reaction,
                copying,
                invention,
                research_time,
                research_material
            )
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::INTEGER[],
                $2::REAL[],
                $3::REAL[],
                $4::REAL[],
                $5::REAL[],
                $6::REAL[],
                $7::REAL[]
            )
